---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import thirty_three from "../images/33.jpg";
---

<Layout title='Media'>

  <section>
    <h2>Media</h2>
    <ul class='list'>
      <li>
        Co-directed and co-produced “Man on a Mission: The Transformative Power
        of the Arts” (2023). Winner of “Best Documentary” (The Golden Door
        International Film Festival) and “Merit Award” (Impact Docs);
      </li>
      <li>
        Author of 2 award winning books:<br />
        <ul>
          <li>
            Mediating the Muse: A Communications Approach to Music, Technology
            and Culture (2020);
          </li>
          <li>
            The Arts and Play as Educational Media in the Digital Age (2020);
          </li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li>President of the Media Ecology Association (2024-2025);</li>
      <li>Taught Media Arts at New Jersey City University (1997-present)</li>
    </ul>
  </section>
  <section class="image-wrapper">
    <div class='text-wrapper'>
      <h2>Man on a Mission: The Transformative Power of the Arts.</h2>
      <div class='text'>
        The recent winner of &quot;Best Documentary&quot; at the Golden Door
        International Film Festival and “Merit Award” from Impact Docs, Man on a
        Mission tells the remarkable story of Carmine Tabone who embarked on a
        forty-five year journey using the arts as a means of building
        community and teaching literacy with young people in Jersey City. The
        documentary explores Tabone’s artistic philosophy which is deceptively
        simple and yet profound. Rather than being the exclusive talent of the
        gifted few, the arts are really a way for healthy communities to form,
        solidify and prosper.
      </div>
    </div>
    <picture class='image'>
      <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/badyim8gKOQ?si=Xc4X6wcGdgemb3Sd" title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe>

    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .image-wrapper {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 2rem 0 0 0;

    > h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: var(--text1);
      font-family: var(--font-serif);
    }
  }
  section {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 2rem 0 0 0;

    > h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: var(--text1);
      font-family: var(--font-serif);
    }
  }

  .list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
    font-family: var(--sans-serif);

    > li {
      line-height: 2;
      font-size: 1.35rem;
    }
  }

  .text-wrapper {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    flex: 1;
    > h2 {
      font-size: 1.75rem;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: var(--text1);
      font-family: var(--font-serif);
    }

    .text {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      color: var(--text1);
      font-family: var(--font-sans);
    }
  }

  .image {
    flex: 1.25;
    
    > video {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
    }
    > img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      min-height: 500px;
      object-fit: cover;
    }
  }

  @media only screen and (min-width: 768px) {
    .image-wrapper {
      flex-direction: row;
      gap: 2rem;
      padding: 5rem 0;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }

    .text {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }
  }

  iframe {
    width: 100%;
    height: 400px;
    object-fit: cover;
  }
</style>
